  {
    "bbox": [
      573,
      1417,
      1205,
      1511
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nf(10) = \\int_{0}^{10} g(t)dt = \\int_{0}^{7} g(t)dt + \\int_{7}^{10} g(t)dt\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      235,
      1522,
      842,
      1615
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Vì trên $[0; 7]$, $g(t) \\ge 0$ nên $\\int_{0}^{7} g(t)dt = S_1$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      235,
      1620,
      895,
      1712
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Vì trên $[7; 10]$, $g(t) \\le 0$ nên $\\int_{7}^{10} g(t)dt = -S_2$."
